Ability.Description: Your creature slams into an enemy hitting all hostiles 4m around the enemy target dealing <<1>> kinetic damage to up to 5 targets.

Ability.Name: Go for the Throat
Ability.Description: Your creature leaps at a target with less than 30% health and sinks in, dealing <<1>> internal damage.

Ability.Name: Headbutt
Ability.Description: Your creature uses its head, stunning the target for 5 seconds.

Ability.Name: Power Bite
Ability.Description: Your creature lunges at the target and delivers a powerful bite, dealing <<1>> internal damage and causes the target to become immobilized.

Ability.Name: Cutting Swipe
Ability.Description: Your creature cuts the target by dealing <<1>> internal damage over a 10 second duration.

Ability.Name: Kolto Collar Scan
Ability.Description: Your creature uses its Kolto Collar to heal a friendly target for <<1>> over 3 seconds.

Ability.Name: Kolto Collar Dart
Ability.Description: Your creature fires a Kolto Dart from its collar, healing the target for <<1>>.

Ability.Name: Affectionate Hairball
Ability.Description: Your creature shows its affection by lavishing slobber on the target healing and cleansing it of mental and physical effects for <<1>> for 10 seconds. What an incredible smell!

Ability.Name: Deafening Roar
Ability.Description: Your creature unleashes a mighty roar that dazes the target for up to 8 seconds. Damage to the target causes this effect to end prematurely. Targets may only be affected by Deafening Roar once every 30 seconds. Target must not be suffering from periodic damage and have greater than 90% max health.

Ability.Name: Collar Kolto Shield
Ability.Description: Your creature uses its collar to place a Kolto-powered shield around the target, preventing a moderate amount of damage for up to 20 seconds.

Ability.Name: Overcharge Collar
Ability.Description: Your creature's collar overcharges unleashing an electric discharge dealing <<1>> internal damage to up to 5 enemies 5m around the impact. Generates a moderate amount of threat and reduces incoming damage by 50% for 10 seconds. Does not hit sleeping, lifted, or incapacitated enemies.

Ability.Name: Multi-Grapple
Ability.Description: Fires a multi-grapple line from your creature's collar that fires in a wide cone in front of the Akk Dog and pulls the closest three targets and generates a high amount of threat. Cannot be used on targets in cover or on targets with Boss Immunity.

Ability.Name: Unleashed Roar
Ability.Description: Your creature taunts attacking enemies forcing them to attack your creature and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Power Charge
Ability.Description: Your creature lunges at the target and delivers a powerful headswipe, dealing <<1>> weapon damage, heals for 25% of damage dealt and generates a moderate amount of threat.

Ability.Name: Prideful Taunt
Ability.Description: Taunts the target, forcing it to attack your creature for 6 seconds. Also reinforces your creature by placing an absorb shield that absorbs a moderate amount of damage.

Ability.Name: Trick: Play Dead
Ability.Description: Your creature plays dead at your 'command'. No creatures were hurt while performing this trick.

Ability.Name: Trick: Preen
Ability.Description: Your creature cleans and further grooms its vicious claws and fur.

Ability.Name: Life Day Snowball Cannon
Ability.Description: Fire a Life Day Snowball Bomb at your target within 30 meters, which explodes in a cloud of snow. Targets will trail snow for a short time after being hit.

Ability.Name: Czerka Z-3B
Ability.Description:
Activates the Czerka Z-3B, increasing movement speed and offering excellent protection against being knocked off. Movement speed increases based on the rank of your Speeder Piloting skill.
Speeder Piloting Rank 1: 90% Speeder Piloting Rank 2: 100% Speeder Piloting Rank 3: 110%

Ability.Name: Dasta Colossus
Ability.Description:
Activates the Dasta Colossus, increasing movement speed and offering excellent protection against being knocked off. Movement speed increases based on the rank of your Speeder Piloting skill.
Speeder Piloting Rank 1: 90% Speeder Piloting Rank 2: 100% Speeder Piloting Rank 3: 110%

Ability.Name: Jungle Gundark
Ability.Description:
Calls your Jungle Gundark mount. Movement speed increases based on the rank of your Speeder Piloting skill.
Speeder Piloting Rank 1: 90% Speeder Piloting Rank 2: 100% Speeder Piloting Rank 3: 110%

Ability.Name: Snowstorm Assault Speeder
Ability.Description:
Activates the Snowstorm Assault Speeder, increasing movement speed and offering excellent protection against being knocked off. Movement speed increases based on the rank of your Speeder Piloting skill. Use the Mount Flourish Key binding to activate this mount's flourish.
Speeder Piloting Rank 1: 90% Speeder Piloting Rank 2: 100% Speeder Piloting Rank 3: 110%

Ability.Name: Force Leap
Ability.Description: Jumps to a distant target, dealing <<1>> damage with the main-hand weapon, immoblizing the target for 2 seconds and interrupting the target's current action. Builds 3 focus. Cannot be used against targets in cover.
